      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.7/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/188c31e8-4730-11e1-9a77-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 23 tests.  1 tests failed: ost-pools.",
